query:
SELECT m.id, m.conversationId, m.direction, m.content, m.createdAt 
FROM messages m 
JOIN conversations c ON m.conversationId = c.id 
WHERE c.merchantId = 150001 AND m.direction = 'incoming'
ORDER BY m.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 5;
